  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA36">
<l>avaṉā mivaṉā muvaṉāmaṟ ṟumpa</l>
<l>ravaṉā mavaṉeṉ ṟirātē yavaṉā</l>
<l>mavaṉē yeṉatteḷintu kaṇṇaṉukkē tīrntā</l>
<l>lavaṉē yevaṉēlu mām.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“He is that one, he is this one, he is the one there, [or] again he is</l>
<l>the one beyond”, without constantly saying so, if, understanding that</l>
<l>he is that one, one is not separated from Kaṇṇaṉ alone,</l>
<l>he is who ever he may be.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
